<h2>What's New in 1.9.10</h2>  <ul><li><strong>Settings redesigned</strong> — Accounts moved to the top of Settings so sign-in and sign-out are always easy to find; notification sections are now named per service with threshold alerts consolidated into a single toggle per window (instead of three separate ones)</li> <li><strong>Settings window fixed</strong> — the window reliably opens at the correct size for all users, including those upgrading from earlier versions where macOS had saved a smaller frame</li></ul>
